</div></p> <p style=3D"margin-left:1.0in;text-indent:-.25in">=C2=B7&nbsp;&n=
bsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Torn or incomplete fins</p> <p sty=
le=3D"margin-left:1.0in;text-indent:-.25in">=C2=B7&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&=
