xt-indent:-.25in">=C2=B7&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Cl=
oudy or bulging eyes (unless bulging eyes happen to be normal=E2=80=94as wi=
th bubble-eye goldfish)</p> <p style=3D"margin-left:1.0in;text-indent:-.25i=
n">=C2=B7&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Necrotic ulcers o=
r lesions<div class=3D"component plain-html col-12 d-lg-none">
